snippet.title: Version Kiana: From Finality, the Origin Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is ascending to Version Kiana: From Finality, the Origin!
The new Herrscher battlesuit Herrscher of Finality for Kiana Kaslana and Raiden Mei's S-rank battlesuit Herrscher of Origin debut!
Plus, the finale to the main story part 1 with special bonuses
and featured event Bustling Holiday Symphony :|| are also coming. Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Kiana Kaslana: Rie Kugimiya
Raiden Mei: Miyuki Sawashiro
Kevin Kaslana: Satoshi Hino
